OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixture of bright spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, the showers heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes and wintry on hills. Feeling
OL,8,Fchilly in the fresh to strong westerly
OL,9,Fwinds. The showers becoming lighter
OL,10,Fand more scattered later in the day
OL,11,Fwith winds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers dying out but
OL,14,Fthickening cloud bringing patchy light
OL,15,Frain to the west coast later this
OL,16,Fevening. The patchy light rain
OL,17,Fextending eastwards overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
