OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FThe west staying mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy, but much of the light rain and
OL,7,Fdrizzle dying out. Brighter spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping around Inverness and the
OL,9,FMoray Firth and feeling quite warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FOutbreaks of rain on Wednesday, heavy
OL,13,Fat times and turning to snow over the
OL,14,Fmountains. Mainly dry on Thursday and
OL,15,FFriday, brightest in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
